{"tid":1638841,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[急] 你屋企樓下條街要人！！","createTime":"2019-10-08T12:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T17:48:36.000Z","uid":228493,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b577aa873bc357326fdc705d4536be8289940de5","tid":1638841,"uid":228493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"唔該你地唔好配合對家搞宵禁 好似縮入老母個閪咁準時縮返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好理黨鐵8點罷駛 唔駛理垃圾罐頭連鎖店早收<br />\n<br />\n同我出曬黎幫襯肯照常開門獨立大小店 出黎掃街睇戲拍拖 有開既地方同我填滿佢(eg. 葵廣 過半有開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>完全係難得可以消費落本土街坊經濟既機會</strong></span><br />\n市道差左 但係冇左連鎖爭生意 係咪應該支持下小生意既生計同耐力呀 街坊舖服務對象係我地班陀地呀<br />\n<br />\n話比罐頭餐廳同垃圾黨鐵知 香港冇左你係無撚所謂 早少少出門迫車都唔會割呀<br />\n<br />\n仲可以保護埋夜晚出動既手足 眾目睽睽人強馬壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n波士頓馬拉松恐襲之後果晚 當地市民係大大力高調出街如常食飯<br />\n就係話比恐怖份子聽 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔會驚出夜街 唔會向白色恐怖低頭</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"538f665367654ca89f31ec723669785d5bf33a07","tid":1638841,"uid":228493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"2ff8b5b7f8263990b35f33926fa4bbcca8bb6489","tid":1638841,"uid":288348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55d05b6aa0f07fd2965942a77611bf94c80dd7a","tid":1638841,"uid":228493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7d86fda483f0d59a4619d850376b5a513ccc8109","tid":1638841,"uid":228493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"624c3c18c5bfcfe1f5916e1e86e92d